{"tid":24511,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做左三年幾酒店炒散 你問我答","createTime":"2016-12-05T14:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T16:20:34.000Z","uid":14819,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c1c6306df892475e1765b414744afa203534ed","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:39:44.000Z","msg":"三年幾都係做宴會部 不過其他餐廳既野都略知一二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有幾會比人起底唔會答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a6f785d53f6a1949536424025e786555fed40c","tid":24511,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"係咪好多大學生intern"},{"pid":"57b4464b2321467cb8cb02e16251a59483fb0514","tid":24511,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:45:38.000Z","msg":"難唔難？係咪手腳要好快？ 想試下炒散"},{"pid":"1e6d8b263397f2adc99fcb40ab3366975aa225ff","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪好多大學生intern</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平均每間餐廳都有一個 不過我做個間酒店比較國際化 咩國家既intern都有 最近黎左個俄妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0814d8e719e594dc60c970eae26d9e79f41027f8","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>難唔難？係咪手腳要好快？ 想試下炒散</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老生常談啦 快少少唔洗比人屌<br />\n不過都係經驗問題 做熟左就知咩要做先 咩唔洗做住 咁就自然會快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8d5d98ee7ba86cdec87ea45edf94f03ce1bab0","tid":24511,"uid":42660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"邊個場最爛"},{"pid":"df0591975a1ea870b037dbea284e6eb22523b46b","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個場最爛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港咁多間酒店 我真係唔知邊個場最爛喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係知唔夠炒散翻工既場好爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fdf289bfb7faaeffdd23a09a6b7dc8f9394b6e","tid":24511,"uid":21672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:55:58.000Z","msg":"最高幾錢個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04fe044a897046b59fb20d149dd88c03d2770a6","tid":24511,"uid":741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"隻手有無事"},{"pid":"119b27ee41bf4fa09e2a0805bfc2e1965ad7f4e2","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最高幾錢個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果有special event 可能去到成100蚊個鐘 不過唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6a78b4819ae128074f1484c261fe95e6dcdd82","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻手有無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n翻炒散可能好過去做gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91acff2528c2c017ece7d771cfcc2acac6a32ee","tid":24511,"uid":42660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"跟開邊個蛇頭"},{"pid":"e093a2231a76769564ef2d85a8375bdf31106690","tid":24511,"uid":42660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"炒散依家有工半未"},{"pid":"c2d145ee56ce6a5b7ef69f3aeddc93b3b60e09d9","tid":24511,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:57:15.000Z","msg":"炒散比狗做 仲要做成三年"},{"pid":"72eb227fca59950cc7e59977ca2e30bc61cc41f7","tid":24511,"uid":32009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"返過邊間最'柒'"},{"pid":"bd5e42598d0b2a299ffa5870421233013be06d98","tid":24511,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪好多大學生intern</blockquote>平均每間餐廳都有一個 不過我做個間酒店比較國際化 咩國家既intern都有 最近黎左個俄妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽過有個poly仔做緊intern去第二間秘撈炒散"},{"pid":"30c544a248d7ca7616ec95733fdc449fe516eb58","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟開邊個蛇頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0342100bc9c84f5f7a71b455b062870b93a6d00","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒散依家有工半未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平安夜 聖誕同埋除夕夜有工半"},{"pid":"d351293a1e7f4df6b2b137657032cc38ca016573","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒散比狗做 仲要做成三年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學生去做算係咁啦 畢左業就唔會做"},{"pid":"2e667c73ad9f0dee8db7a09abdaed281b2db6a97","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返過邊間最'柒'</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n翻過某間係新界區既酒店 都好柒下 翻到去擺下位 抹下野就一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a819503748923200efda3c2279ee6a117d955e73","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T18:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪好多大學生intern</blockquote>平均每間餐廳都有一個 不過我做個間酒店比較國際化 咩國家既intern都有 最近黎左個俄妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>聽過有個poly仔做緊intern去第二間秘撈炒散</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIntern張contract比唔比秘撈我真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都見過d full time staff放假都會炒下散"},{"pid":"d35e32e4d9a4f486e57c8b67251b0d3e025337eb","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T01:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd2ecb4e3a5d4c3e8acff54e90879c7b3800c51","tid":24511,"uid":52936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:09:48.000Z","msg":"如果全職有幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c97526ee582c6c3888d720048ca7d131f6fd978","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果全職有幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果當一個月翻24日 每日十個鐘咁計 一個月大約有萬四至萬六左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d181847f3e49980b1649c6acdec63d4dff78dd","tid":24511,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"讀書果陣都做過兩年<br />\n都識到好多酒肉朋友😂<br />\n有D到依家都仲做緊，有D轉左長工"},{"pid":"3de7daefb513de17e4348b9ef6312c1f15888da4","tid":24511,"uid":52936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:43:53.000Z","msg":"我有fd一路做做到部長，部長有幾銀？<br />\n見佢好似撈得幾好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f022233be38299b61ec1cd34062e1d8c7ecad9c6","tid":24511,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:46:52.000Z","msg":"屌 做炒散呢d濕鳩工都可以開你問我答 收檔啦"},{"pid":"30541af0a89217218c873a881803e86324211808","tid":24511,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有fd一路做做到部長，部長有幾銀？<br />\n見佢好似撈得幾好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下邊到部長 高級酒店西餐 大約18000-20000 但多數間餐廳係幾出名先有呢個價 其他普通d咪15000 但做到隻狗咁 一日十粒鐘 on9工"},{"pid":"67930dc0ae278d382a710844a89cf4e3d211594e","tid":24511,"uid":52936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有fd一路做做到部長，部長有幾銀？<br />\n見佢好似撈得幾好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下邊到部長 高級酒店西餐 大約18000-20000 但多數間餐廳係幾出名先有呢個價 其他普通d咪15000 但做到隻狗咁 一日十粒鐘 on9工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似過十粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd1de491d8fdf91b1c0430452b1f979227481e8","tid":24511,"uid":17401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:11:21.000Z","msg":"最甘試過一個人打幾多圍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebdc6de22057ae7cdebd531e9455b31ee484d6e","tid":24511,"uid":2467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T04:01:24.000Z","msg":"有當年會考出黎做既朋友都升曬上manager級既位。"},{"pid":"2d6f754d0fe1beca5d299b8fa89de424b5a433d6","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 做炒散呢d濕鳩工都可以開你問我答 收檔啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我認係濕鳩工黎 不過唔開 人地又點知呢行有幾咁濕鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40718ad6412b59fd5640ac89b5495d44ff649752","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有fd一路做做到部長，部長有幾銀？<br />\n見佢好似撈得幾好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下邊到部長 高級酒店西餐 大約18000-20000 但多數間餐廳係幾出名先有呢個價 其他普通d咪15000 但做到隻狗咁 一日十粒鐘 on9工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似過十粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人工係巴打講既差唔多 而家d部長份約就寫9個鐘/10個鐘 但係日日至少都ot到12個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2227f50acc082bf032760b054468a74bb1e0234b","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最甘試過一個人打幾多圍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個人做4圍中菜 一個分菜 一個做枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc8a171d75c6283ab30ce43c3f46c5e3261bbf4","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有當年會考出黎做既朋友都升曬上manager級既位。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個經理位係要用體力同精神換翻黎"},{"pid":"d01d02c605ea028938829e188989b356398bb82c","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12abdfb19681c6560fb98ad9ca9458dafe2c82e","tid":24511,"uid":3449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"之前in過某酒店炒散，哇in人果個呀伯串到馬撚咁，洗唔洗咁高姿態呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc0fe599114220a61ed8ba6b91bddc6e4115613","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前in過某酒店炒散，哇in人果個呀伯串到馬撚咁，洗唔洗咁高姿態呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係想比姿態你睇 其實佢心入面幾撚想人翻工"},{"pid":"35b07cc66eb044d0cdd2736f5ef113b000a0735d","tid":24511,"uid":22501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f1933637d22774ea9bd75b12d37c6c0c443acff","tid":24511,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"狗都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73559e7d3863181e483d24082f313ceb710021fb","tid":24511,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T13:41:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾 仲要做三年"},{"pid":"45b2b5527ba043d7e36b351d4115d08a1d2bb906","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇做過如心？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60628196032cc17412adbe1ef7c03c0bc4c42aa1","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做行行都係做狗架啦 咩都係比老闆屌同比客屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你係老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd22edd1235e7bd1d6d3316385554a4c2fad0b7","tid":24511,"uid":6495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前in過某酒店炒散，哇in人果個呀伯串到馬撚咁，洗唔洗咁高姿態呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炒散都要in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03963a8f086fe6abcef1ec2468f063cdfb18a6b9","tid":24511,"uid":30315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:56:21.000Z","msg":"點睇有啲人長炒"},{"pid":"1a20c2a102ca469d37ce29158724d2304e0d0c2c","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾 仲要做三年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都係個句 我認呢份係西工<br />\n只能夠講呢份工既工作時間同人工係幾符合我呢d學生哥既要求<br />\nBtw 有無d高人工又啱學生做既工介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee91e8a7e834a518460b351e40699c0ff469492a","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前in過某酒店炒散，哇in人果個呀伯串到馬撚咁，洗唔洗咁高姿態呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炒散都要in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫做見下經理 比佢了解下你有無相關既工作經驗 最主要都係了解下你適唔適合做呢行<br />\n見過有d人in 叫佢用幾句介紹下自己 點知佢勁騰雞 連自己叫咩名都講唔出 試問呢d人點做服務性行業"},{"pid":"10329be6f0579b58b432924c253bdc869e880a50","tid":24511,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"番學玩過 決定讀書一世唔會再做waiter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c53e4c3dfe90ab26f74ddbb8e883393009c1ea","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點睇有啲人長炒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長炒可以歸類成三種既:呀叔，家庭主婦，後生仔女<br />\n呀叔:無其他工作技能 淨係識炒散<br />\n家庭主婦:每日做幾個鐘 當幫補家計<br />\n後生仔女:好多時佢地都係無乜工作上既期盼 當自己係做freelance 可以隨時去旅行"},{"pid":"a29bd9eb1168e5d1c0bcc9f4cf0559c6f516869e","tid":24511,"uid":14819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>番學玩過 決定讀書一世唔會再做waiter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我暑假工做過物流業 日曬雨淋 我都同自己講過 一世都唔再做呢行"}]}